                <p class="cs-row-text">Grief & Trauma Theory & Kids Hurt Too Hawaii Program Model; Awareness and Self Exploration (8 hours) 9-5pm</p>
            </div>
             <div class="cs-row">
                <h3 class="cs-row-title">TBD</h3>
